  <entry>
    <title>Windows下安装JDK、Tomcat、Maven与配置</title>
    <link href="/2023/07/17/Windows%E4%B8%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85JDK%E3%80%81Maven%E3%80%81Tomcat%E4%B8%8E%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <url>/2023/07/17/Windows%E4%B8%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85JDK%E3%80%81Maven%E3%80%81Tomcat%E4%B8%8E%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Windows下安装JDK、Tomcat、Maven与配置"><a href="#Windows下安装JDK、Tomcat、Maven与配置" class="headerlink" title="Windows下安装JDK、Tomcat、Maven与配置"></a>Windows下安装JDK、Tomcat、Maven与配置</h1><h2 id="一、JDK的下载与环境变量配置"><a href="#一、JDK的下载与环境变量配置" class="headerlink" title="一、JDK的下载与环境变量配置"></a>一、JDK的下载与环境变量配置</h2><h3 id="1-1-下载jdk1-8"><a href="#1-1-下载jdk1-8" class="headerlink" title="1.1 下载jdk1.8"></a>1.1 下载jdk1.8</h3><p>官网链接：<a href="https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/#java8-windows">https://www.oracle.com/java/technologies/downloads/#java8-windows</a></p><p><img src="/../img/oracle-jdk-8.png"></p><p>根据系统选择对应版本即可</p><h3 id="1-2-安装"><a href="#1-2-安装" class="headerlink" title="1.2 安装"></a>1.2 安装</h3><p>双击下载好的安装包，建议更改一下安装路径，其他下一步即可，此处不在赘述。</p><h3 id="1-3-配置环境变量"><a href="#1-3-配置环境变量" class="headerlink" title="1.3 配置环境变量"></a>1.3 配置环境变量</h3><p>右键【此电脑】-&gt;【属性】-&gt;【高级系统设置】-&gt;【新建系统变量】<br><strong>(1) JAVA_HOME</strong></p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">变量名：JAVA_HOME变量值：E:\Development\Java\jdk1.8.0_311（为jdk的安装目录，根据实际情况）<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>如下图所示：</p><p><img src="/../img/win-jdk-sys-path.png"></p><p><strong>(2) CLASSPATH</strong></p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">变量名：CLASSPATH变量值： .;%JAVA_HOME%\lib;%JAVA_HOME%\lib\tools.jar<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>如下图所示：</p><p><img src="/../img/win-jdk-classpath.png"></p><p><strong>(3) 系统变量下的path变量</strong></p><figure><div class="code-wrapper"><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">新建：%JAVA_HOME%\bin新建：%JAVA_HOME%\jre\bin<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre></div></figure><p>如下图所示：</p><p><img src="/../img/win-jdk-path.png"></p><h3 id="1-4-验证"><a href="#1-4-验证" class="headerlink" title="1.4 验证"></a>1.4 验证</h3><p>WIN + R打开cmd命令行窗口，输入<code>java -version</code>和<code>javac -version</code>，出现如下图所示，则JDK配置成功。</p><p><img src="/../img/win-jdk-check.png"></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
